Package: scPlotSimplex
Type: Package
Title: Create Simplex Plot to Visualize Cell Fate Similarity of Single Cells
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Jialin Liu [aut, cre],
        Yichen Wang [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Yichen Wang <wayichen@umich.edu>
Description: Create simplex plot to visualize the similarity between 
    single-cells and selected clusters in a binary, ternary or quaternary space.
    Velocity information can be added as an additional layer.
